    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>beef strips </strong>to a large bowl with the <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame oil</strong>, 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside to marinate</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1-1617029793548-x200.jpg",
