            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the beef is marinating, slice the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>onion</strong> finely</p><p>Top, tail peel and chop your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> into thin batons</p><p>Slice your <strong>chestnut mushrooms </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
