    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped vegetables</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until they're tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, transfer them to a plate and set aside for later</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
