        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a high heat</p><p>Once very hot, add the <strong>marinated beef</strong> (with the<strong> remaining marinade</strong>) to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until the beef is browned all over and slightly pink on the inside</p><p>Return the <strong>cooked vegetables</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>beef bulgogi</strong></p>",
