    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Serve the <strong>sticky rice</strong> with the <strong>beef bulgogi</strong> to the side and garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
